cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for person re-identification, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel unsupervised domain adaptation approach, which involves clustering and synthesizing large-scale environments, indicating a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image and video benchmark datasets, indicating a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and potentially cryptography (cs.CR) for secure re-identification.
